msgstr "kdebase"

#: index.docbook:430
msgid ""
"This package contains the base applications that form the core of the K "
"Desktop Environment like the window manager, the terminal emulator, the "
"control center, the file manager, and the panel."
msgstr ""
"Dieses Paket enth&auml;lt die Standardanwendungen, die den Kern der "
"&kde;-Arbeitsumgebung bilden; den Fenstermanager, den Terminal-Emulator, das "
"Kontrollzentrum, den Dateimanager und die Kontrollleiste."

#: index.docbook:430
msgid "kdegames"
msgstr "kdegames"

# index.docbook:463, index.docbook:471, index.docbook:479, index.docbook:487, index.docbook:494, index.docbook:502, index.docbook:509, index.docbook:516
