"Verschiedene Schreibtischutensilien wie Taschenrechner, Editor und anderes."

#: index.docbook:430
msgid "kdemultimedia"
msgstr "kdemultimedia"

#: index.docbook:430
msgid "Multimedia applications like a &CD; player and a mixer."
msgstr "Multimediaanwendungen wie &CD;-Spieler und Mixer (Mischpult)."

#: index.docbook:430
msgid "kdenetwork"
msgstr "kdenetwork"

#: index.docbook:430
msgid ""
"Network applications. Currently contains the mail program, the news reader, "
"and several other network-related programs."
msgstr ""
"Netzwerkanwendungen. Zur Zeit enth&auml;t dieses Paket das E-Mail-Programm, "
"den Newsreader und einige andere Programme zum Thema Netzwerke."

#: index.docbook:430
msgid "kdeadmin"
msgstr "kdeadmin"

#: index.docbook:430
msgid "System administration programs."
msgstr "Systemverwaltungsprogramme."

#: index.docbook:430
msgid "kdetoys"
msgstr "kdetoys"

#: index.docbook:430
msgid "Toys!"
msgstr "Nette Kleinigkeiten, Spielzeuge."

#: index.docbook:430
msgid "&korganizer;"
msgstr "&korganizer;"

#: index.docbook:430
msgid "Your desktop would never be complete without an organizer, right?"
msgstr "Kein Schreibtisch ist komplett ohne Organizer, richtig?"

#: index.docbook:522
msgid ""
"kdesupport (if needed) should be installed before everything else. The next "
"(or first) package should be kdelibs. The other packages can be installed in "
"any arbitrary order."
msgstr ""
"kdesupport (wenn notwendig) sollten Sie vor allen anderen Paketen "
