"installiert werden. Alle anderen Pakete k&ouml;nnen in beliebiger "
"Reihenfolge installiert werden."

#: index.docbook:530
msgid "Installation instructions for the different package formats"
msgstr "Installationsanleitung f&uuml;r die verschiedenen Paketformate"

#: index.docbook:534
msgid ""
"Please do not forget to read the <filename>README</filename> and "
"<filename>INSTALL</filename> files if they are available."
msgstr ""
"Lesen Sie unbedingt die Dateien <filename>README</filename> und "
"<filename>INSTALL</filename>."

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "Installation of the Debian packages"
msgstr "Installation von Debianpaketen"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"The Debian packages install according to the upcoming FHS (File Hierarchy "
"Standard)."
msgstr ""
"Die Debianpakete installieren sich entsprechend dem kommenden FHS (File "
"Hierarchy Standard)."

# index.docbook:545, index.docbook:557, index.docbook:564, index.docbook:608
#: index.docbook:538
msgid "become superuser"
msgstr "Melden Sie sich mit Systemverwalterrechten an."

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"run <command>dpkg <option>-i "
"<replaceable>packagename.deb</replaceable></option></command> for every "
"package you want to install."
msgstr ""
"run <command>dpkg <option>-i "
"<replaceable>packagename.deb</replaceable></option></command> for every "
"package you want to install."

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "Installation of the <acronym>RPM</acronym> packages"
msgstr "Installation von <acronym>RPM</acronym> Paketen"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "To install binary <acronym>RPM</acronym>s"
msgstr "Installieren von bin&auml;ren <acronym>RPM</acronym>s"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"execute <command>rpm <option>-ivh "
"<replaceable>packagename.rpm</replaceable></option></command>"
msgstr ""
"F&uuml;hren Sie den folgenden Befehl aus: <command>rpm <option>-ivh "
"<replaceable>packagename.rpm</replaceable></option></command>"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"To create and install a binary <acronym>RPM</acronym> from the source "
"<acronym>RPM</acronym>"
msgstr ""
"Erzeugen und Installieren eines bin&auml;ren <acronym>RPM</acronym>-Paketes "
"aus Quellen"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"run <command>rpm <option>-ivh "
"<replaceable>packagename.src.rpm</replaceable></option></command>"
msgstr ""
"F&uuml;hren Sie folgendene Befehle aus: <command>rpm <option>-ivh "
"<replaceable>packagename.src.rpm</replaceable></option></command>"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "cd /usr/src/redhat/SPECS"
msgstr "cd /usr/src/redhat/SPECS"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "rpm <option>-bb <replaceable>packagename.spec</replaceable></option>"
msgstr "rpm <option>-bb <replaceable>packagename.spec</replaceable></option>"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"<command>cd ../RPMS/<replaceable>i386</replaceable></command> (or whatever "
"architecture you use)"
msgstr ""
"<command>cd ../RPMS/<replaceable>i386</replaceable></command> (f&uml;r "
"welche Architektur Sie nutzen)"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"rpm <option>-ivh <replaceable>packagename.i386.rpm</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"rpm <option>-ivh <replaceable>packagename.i386.rpm</replaceable> </option>"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "Installation of the source <filename>.tar.gz</filename> files"
msgstr "Installation von Quellen <filename>.tar.gz</filename>-Dateien"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"The source <filename>.tgz</filename> package installs into <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/local/kde</filename> by default. You can override "
"this setting by using the <option>--prefix</option> option of the "
"<filename>configure</filename> script."
msgstr ""
"Die Quellen <filename>.tgz</filename>-Pakete installieren sich "
"standardm&auml;&szlig;ig in das Verzeichnis <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/local/kde</filename>. Dies k&ouml;nnen Sie manuell "
"ver&auml;ndern, indem Sie die <option>--prefix</option> Option des "
"\"<filename>configure</filename>\"-Skripts benutzen."

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"unpack the packages with <command>tar <option>xvzf "
"<replaceable>packagename.tar.gz</replaceable></option></command>"
msgstr ""
"Entpacken Sie die Pakete mit <command>tar <option>xvzf "
"<replaceable>packagename.tar.gz</replaceable></option></command>"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"change directory to the package directory: <command>cd "
"<replaceable>packagename</replaceable></command>"
msgstr ""
"Wechseln Sie in das Verzeichnis des Paketes: <command>cd "
"<replaceable>packagename</replaceable></command>"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "configure the package: <command>./configure</command>"
msgstr "Konfigurieren Sie das Paket mit: <command>make</command>"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"Some packages (notably kdebase) have special configuration options that "
"might be applicable to your installation. Type <command>./configure "
"<option>--help</option></command> to see the available options."
msgstr ""
"Einige Pakete (vor allem kdebase) haben spezielle Optionen, die f&uuml;r "
"Ihre Installation notwendig sein k&ouml;nnen. Geben Sie <command>./configure "
"<option>--help</option></command> ein, um die vorhandenen Optionen angezeigt "
"zu bekommen."

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "build the package: <command>make</command>"
msgstr "Erstellen Sie das Paket mit: <command>make</command>"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"install the package: <command>su <option>-c \"make "
"install\"</option></command> (if you aren't already root). If you already "
"are, just type <command>make <option>install</option></command>."
msgstr ""
"Installieren Sie das Paket mit <command>su <option>-c \"make "
"install\"</option></command> (Wenn Sie noch nicht mit Systemverwalterrechten "
"angemeldet sind). Wenn Sie schon als Systemverwalter angemeldet sind, dann "
"geben Sie ein: <command>make<option> install</option></command>."

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "Installation of the binary <filename>.tar.gz</filename> files"
msgstr "Installation von bin&auml;ren <filename>.tar.gz</filename> Dateien"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid ""
"The binary .tar.gz package installs into <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/opt/kde</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Die bin&auml;ren .tar.gz Pakete installieren sich in das Verzeichnis "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/opt/kde</filename>."

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "cd /"
msgstr "cd /"

#: index.docbook:538
msgid "tar <option>xvzf <replaceable>packagename.tar.gz</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"tar <option>xvzf <replaceable>packagename.tar.gz</replaceable></option>"

#: index.docbook:620
msgid "Post-installation procedures"
msgstr "Nach-Installations Prozeduren"

#: index.docbook:623
msgid ""
"First of all, please make sure that you have added &kde;'s binary "
"installation directory (<abbrev>e.g.</abbrev> <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/opt/kde/bin</filename>) to your <envar>PATH</envar> and "
"&kde;'s library installation directory to your "
"<envar>LD_LIBRARY_PATH</envar> (only necessary on systems that do not "
"support rpath; on &Linux; &ELF;, it should work without). This environment "
"variable may be called differently on some systems, <abbrev>e.g.</abbrev> it "
"is called <envar>SHLIB_PATH</envar> on &IRIX;. Then set the environment "
"variable <envar>KDEDIR</envar> to the base of your &kde; tree, "
"<abbrev>e.g.</abbrev> <filename class=\"directory\">/opt/kde</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Stellen Sie zuerst sicher, dass das bin&auml;re "
"&kde;-Installationsverzeichnis (<abbrev>z.B.</abbrev> <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/opt/kde/bin</filename>) zu Ihrem <envar>PATH</envar> "
"und das &kde;-Library-Installationsverzeichnis zu Ihrem "
"<envar>LD_LIBRARY_PATH</envar> hinzugef&uuml;gt wurde. Dies gilt nur "
"f&uuml;r Systeme, die rpath nicht unterst&uuml;tzen; auf &Linux; &ELF;, "
"sollte es auch ohne dieses Hinzuf&uuml;gen funktionieren. Diese "
"Umgebungsvariable kann auf verschiedenen Systemen unterschiedlich bezeichnet "
"sein; <abbrev>z.B.</abbrev> sie hei&szlig;t <envar>SHLIB_PATH</envar> auf "
"&IRIX;. Setzen Sie die Umgebungsvariable <envar>KDEDIR</envar> dann auf die "
"Basis Ihres &kde;-Verzeichnisbaumes, <abbrev>z.B.</abbrev> <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/opt/kde</filename>."

#: index.docbook:623
msgid ""
"Please bear in mind that it is unwise to set <envar>LD_LIBRARY_PATH</envar> "
"blindly. In the vast majority of cases it is unnecessary and can do more "
"harm than good. There is a web page written by <ulink "
"url=\"mailto:barr@cis.ohio-state.edu\">Dave Barr</ulink> explaining the "
"evils of <envar>LD_LIBRARY_PATH</envar> and it can be found at <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.cis.ohio-state.edu/~barr/ldpath.html\">http://www.cis.ohio-s"
"tate.edu/~barr/ldpath.html</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Please bear in mind that it is unwise to set <envar>LD_LIBRARY_PATH</envar> "
"blindly. In the vast majority of cases it is unnecessary and can do more "
"harm than good. There is a web page written by <ulink "
"url=\"mailto:barr@cis.ohio-state.edu\">Dave Barr</ulink> explaining the "
"evils of <envar>LD_LIBRARY_PATH</envar> and it can be found at <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.cis.ohio-state.edu/~barr/ldpath.html\">http://www.cis.ohio-s"
"tate.edu/~barr/ldpath.html</ulink>."

#: index.docbook:644
msgid ""
"Even though you can use most of the &kde; applications simply by calling "
"them, you can only benefit fully from &kde;'s advanced features if you use "
"the &kde; window manager and its helper programs."
msgstr ""
"Auch wenn Sie die meisten &kde;-Anwendungen einfach durch Aufrufen beim "
"Namen benutzen k&ouml;nnen, profitieren Sie von &kde;'s weitentwickelten "
"Eigenschaften nur, wenn Sie den &kde;-Fenstermanager und dessen "
"Hilfprogramme benutzen."

#: index.docbook:648
msgid ""
"In order to make it easy for you, we have provided a simple script called "
"<filename>startkde</filename> which gets installed in <filename "
"class=\"directory\">$<envar>KDEDIR</envar>/bin</filename> and is therefore "
"in your path."
